                     <interp inst="t18490129-498-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, stealing 1 handkerchief, value 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18490129-name-355" type="victimName">
