                        <interp inst="t18490129-name-361" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES CAMPBELL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, H</hi> 107). I produce a certificate of Holland's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted March</hi>, 1848, <hi rend="italic">confined six months.</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
